id: pm-8c2s
title: create's schedule-less calendar hint suggests rejected --event pipe form (accepts CSV) — blocks agents
description: "src/cli/commands/create.ts:1927 prints on every schedule-less Event/Reminder/Meeting/Milestone create a hint to run 'pm update ID --event' with a pipe-delimited title|start|end value. The parser REJECTS that and wants CSV key=value (title=,start=,end=). An agent following the CLI's own hint hits a hard error. Fix hint to the real CSV form. Verified live."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: agent-ux,bug,calendar,never-block
created_at: "2026-05-29T22:28:34.206Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-30T05:15:09.786Z"
author: maintainer-agent
resolution: Fixed
close_reason: "create's schedule-less calendar hint now suggests the accepted CSV --event form (start=<ISO>,end=<ISO>) instead of the rejected pipe form."
body: ""
